SUPABASE BEST PRACTICES
CLIENT USAGE
Context Import Why Route handlers, Server Components `createServerClient` from `@supabase/ssr` Reads cookies correctly in server context Client Components (`'use client'`) `createBrowserClient` from `@supabase/ssr` Uses anon key, no service role exposure 
